name: Cat Warfare
description:
NOTE: This game is still a work in progress so some parts of the game will not work or will be missing.Features:
  • Fast-Paced Multiplayer Action.
  • 7 Different Weapons.
  • Lots of environments to fight on.
  • A lot of Cat Customization skins and gear sets.
  • Gore settings for people who don't want gore.
  • Classic Deathmatch.
  • More to come.
Planned Features:
  • Story mode.
  • Bots.
  • More Gamemodes: TeamDeathmatch, Capture the flag, instagib, Etc.
  • More enviroments
